%F A066998 a(n) = (n!)^2*Sum_{i=1..n} 1/(i!)^2.
%F A066998 a(n) = floor((1-BesselI(0, 2))*(n!)^2). - _Benoit Cloitre_, Nov 02 2002
%F A066998 Sum_{n>=0} a(n) * x^n / (n!)^2 = (BesselI(0,2*sqrt(x)) - 1) / (1 - x). - _Ilya Gutkovskiy_, Jan 23 2021
